  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defeat hordes of enemies with up to 4 friends on the multiplayer mode:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/22a82d357a46a733ef6364c27fdd7e75.poster.avif?t=1773334303\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/22a82d357a46a733ef6364c27fdd7e75.webm?t=1773334303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/22a82d357a46a733ef6364c27fdd7e75.mp4?t=1773334303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gather relics, get stronger, and create builds to synergize your powers:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/f17242033a1c09ce67036a736142b775.poster.avif?t=1773334303\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/f17242033a1c09ce67036a736142b775.webm?t=1773334303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/f17242033a1c09ce67036a736142b775.mp4?t=1773334303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Single player or Online Multiplayer with up to 4 players</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• More than 30 unique relics and 10 passive upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Multiple stages and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Unlockable characters.</p>",
